---
import B2BLayout from '../../layouts/B2BLayout.astro';

export async function getStaticPaths() {
  const sampleCollabs = [
    {
      slug: "rimowa",
      partnerName: "RIMOWA",
      partnerLogo: "",
      heroImage: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558618666-fcd25c85cd64?w=1600&q=80",
      projectType: "collab_flavor",
      year: 2023,
      flavorName: "Papaya Sorbet & Mint Cookie Chip",
      published: true,
      body: `
# RIMOWA × Guss Damn Good

When RIMOWA approached us to craft an exclusive flavor for their Bangkok flagship launch, we knew this wasn't just about ice cream — it was about crafting a feeling that matched the precision and elegance of their legendary aluminum cases.

## The Brief

RIMOWA wanted something that felt global yet tropical. Something that spoke to the traveler — always moving, always arriving somewhere new, carrying a little piece of everywhere they've been.

## Story-to-Flavor

We spent three weeks in the kitchen. The answer came from a simple moment: biting into a papaya at a Bangkok street market at 7am, the cool morning air mixing with the fruit's warmth.

Papaya Sorbet & Mint Cookie Chip was born — bright, clean, surprising. Just like opening a RIMOWA case for the first time.

## The Result

Served exclusively at the RIMOWA Bangkok flagship opening event. 400 scoops in 2 hours. Zero left over.
      `
    },
    {
      slug: "valentino",
      partnerName: "Valentino",
      partnerLogo: "",
      heroImage: "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1490481651871-ab68de25d43d?w=1600&q=80",
      projectType: "collab_flavor",
      year: 2023,
      flavorName: "Greek Yogurt Lemon & Black Sesame",
      published: true,
      body: `
# Valentino × Guss Damn Good

A study in contrast. The softness of Greek yogurt against the depth of black sesame. The brightness of lemon against the darkness of the night.

## The Brief

Valentino's creative direction for this collaboration was simple: tension. Light and dark. Past and future. East and West.

## Story-to-Flavor

Greek Yogurt Lemon carries the lightness of Mediterranean afternoons. Black Sesame carries the quiet weight of Asian heritage. Together they are something neither could be alone.

## The Result

Launched at Valentino's exclusive SS23 preview in Bangkok. Featured in Vogue Thailand.
      `
    }
  ];

  return sampleCollabs.map((collab) => ({
    params: { slug: collab.slug },
    props: { collab }
  }));
}

const { collab } = Astro.props;
---

<B2BLayout
  title={`${collab.partnerName} × Guss Damn Good`}
  description={`${collab.partnerName} collaboration — ${collab.flavorName}`}
  partnerName={collab.partnerName}
  partnerLogo={collab.partnerLogo}
  heroImage={collab.heroImage}
  projectType={collab.projectType}
>
  <div class="collab-content">
    <div class="collab-content__meta">
      <span class="collab-meta-tag">{collab.year}</span>
      {collab.flavorName && (
        <span class="collab-meta-tag collab-meta-tag--flavor">
          {collab.flavorName}
        </span>
      )}
    </div>

    <div class="collab-body" set:html={collab.body
      .replace(/^# (.+)$/gm, '<h1>$1</h1>')
      .replace(/^## (.+)$/gm, '<h2>$1</h2>')
      .replace(/\n\n/g, '</p><p>')
    } />
  </div>

  <div class="collab-back">
    <a href="/collabs" class="collab-back__link">
      Back to all collaborations
    </a>
  </div>

</B2BLayout>

<style>
  .collab-content {
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .collab-content__meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .collab-meta-tag {
    padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #555;
  }

  .collab-meta-tag--flavor {
    border-color: rgba(245,230,66,0.2);
    color: #F5E642;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
  }

  .collab-body {
    color: #888;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .collab-back {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
  }

  .collab-back__link {
    color: #444;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .collab-back__link:hover {
    color: #F5E642;
  }
</style>
